			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>Haven't seen any threads on this yet, but I'm really enjoying this game.  It is free to play, and free to download, courtesy of a couple of guys from New Zealand.  There are microtransactions, which they seem to be using to support everything.<br />
<br />
I'm really enjoying it; its still open beta although supposedly there will be no more character resets or wipes.  6 classes, based off 3 stats (int, dex, str).  Very similar to Diablo 2, including waypoints, scrolls for portals and ID, divided into Acts,  and levels of difficulty (normal, cruel, merciless).  There are also events and leagues (sort of like hardcore mode).  Skill tree is massive, and each class starts somewhere different on it.  It is multiplayer much like D3; you will only see other players in hub areas, but your party will go to whatever instanced zone you go to.<br />
<br />
So, if you enjoyed Diablo 2, this is seriously worth the time for being entirely free.  Check it out.  And if someone posted about it and I didn't see, I apologize.<br />
<br />
<a href="http://www.pathofexile.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://www.pathofexile.com/</a></div>

